data.description: Come on in! Welcome to this inviting 3 bed 2 bath home located on a corner lot in the quaint Englewood subdivision in Rocky Mount! This home is minutes away from restaurants, grocery stores, shopping and medical facilities. Walk in and you'll notice the updated features including kitchen lighting and the floating shelves in the living room while keeping the authenticity of the original hardwood flooring. Cuddle up this winter and keep warm in front of the hearth of the all brick fire place while watching your favorite shows. The artistic color palette alone sets this home apart from the rest!
